<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Weft — Your Wardrobe, Elevated</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Nav */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }

    .wordmark {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    nav a.nav-link {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #555;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    nav a.nav-link:hover {
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 72px 24px 80px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 7vw, 56px);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .hero p.subtitle {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #444;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 0 36px;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .app-store-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #888;
      background: #f3f3f3;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      cursor: default;
      letter-spacing: 0.1px;
    }

    /* Features */
    .features {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 16px 24px 96px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 40px 48px;
    }

    .feature h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 650;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      letter-spacing: -0.1px;
    }

    .feature p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #555;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 28px 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #888;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero h1 { letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <a class="wordmark" href="/">Weft</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="/support.html">Support</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Your wardrobe,<br>elevated.</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Weft helps you build a wardrobe that actually works — cataloguing what you own, surfacing outfit ideas, and helping you shop smarter.</p>
    <span class="app-store-badge">Coming to the App Store</span>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Wardrobe</h2>
      <p>Photograph and catalogue every item you own. Track colors, fits, brands, and condition — all in one place.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Style Guide</h2>
      <p>Pick an item and get outfit ideas built around it, tailored to your style and what you already own.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Fit Check</h2>
      <p>Upload a photo of your outfit and get an honest, constructive critique from overall impression to specific styling notes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <h2>Scout</h2>
      <p>Photograph something you are considering buying. Find out whether it fits your wardrobe before you commit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <span>&copy; Switch Development, LLC</span>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="/privacy.html">Privacy</a>
      <a href="/terms.html">Terms</a>
      <a href="/support.html">Support</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
